---
title: Orange Chicken with Jasmine Rice
description: Got an instant craving for restaurant-worthy orange chicken? We know the feeling. Here, our chefs cooked up a special twist on the comforting dish. The star: A delectably sweet and spicy sauce, brightened with freshly squeezed orange juice and Thai chili sauce for a touch of heat. Coated in a light and crispy tempura batter, the chicken is fried to golden brown perfection. One bite will have you thinking “orange I glad I tried this?”
